                        <placeName key="place_101023">CHADDLESWICK</placeName>. <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> le <surname>Norreis</surname>  of <placeName role="person" key="place_101023">Chadleswich</placeName>
                        </persName> grants to the house of the <orgName key="org_101009">hospital of St. Wlstan</orgName>, and the brethren and sisters there, in
               frankalmoigne, a tenement which <persName>
                           <forename>Geoffrey</forename> 
                           <surname>Berde</surname>
                        </persName> held, and a selion of land in <placeName key="place_101052">Sidenhale</placeName>
               towards <placeName key="place_101036">Haliwell</placeName>, and one meadow called Hechelesmedwe, for ever. (<origDate notBefore="1240" notAfter="1250" precision="low">c. 1240-50</origDate>.) <!-- check: 6a? -->. </p>
